      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! Not a scratch or a smudge in sight, and it drives as smooth as the day I got it. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
