    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality, investment-grade example of the A80 chassis, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six. This vehicle remains in a strictly stock configuration, preserving the factory sequential turbocharger mapping and the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The engine bay is immaculate, showing no signs of heat cycling fatigue or aftermarket interference. Power is delivered through the original Torsen limited-slip differential, while the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension retains its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity. All VIN tags are present on original body panels, and the undercarriage reflects a climate-controlled history with zero oxidation. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
