      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, featuring a deep, mirror-like exterior finish entirely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control\u2014operates with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history and a smooth, responsive powertrain that performs exactly as it did on the day of delivery. This is a rare, collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best.",
